  <entry>
    <title>如何將Json存入資料庫當中</title>
    <link href="https://robinsonweng.github.io/2019/09/19/json-to-database/"/>
    <id>https://robinsonweng.github.io/2019/09/19/json-to-database/</id>
    <published>2019-09-19T09:06:30.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-09-23T14:33:49.992Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>有兩種解決的方法</h2><ol><li>在資料庫支援的情況下, 以Documention為輔完成任務</li><li>沒有資料庫不支援的情況下, 將Json的每個key拆開變成獨立的表格, 並加上ID建立所謂的關係來連結不同的表格</li></ol><p><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>data.json</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;id&quot;: &quot;1&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;name&quot;: &quot;Jane&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hobby&quot;:&quot;Cooking&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;Age&quot;: &quot;10&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;Pet&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;name&quot; :&quot;David&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;species&quot;: &quot;Dog&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;age&quot;: &quot;4&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;id&quot;: &quot;2&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;name&quot;: &quot;Lucy&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hobby&quot;:&quot;Jogging&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;Age&quot;: &quot;18&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;Pet&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;name&quot;: &quot;Kitto&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;species&quot;: &quot;Cat&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;age&quot;: &quot;4&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><blockquote><p>Table example:</p></blockquote><p><code>table: Name</code></p><table><thead><tr><th>ID</th><th>Name</th><th style="text-align:left">Hobby</th><th style="text-align:center">Age</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>Jane</td><td style="text-align:left">Cooking</td><td style="text-align:center">10</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>Lucy</td><td style="text-align:left">Jogging</td><td style="text-align:center">18</td></tr></tbody></table><p><code>table: Pet</code></p><table><thead><tr><th>ID</th><th>Name</th><th style="text-align:center">species</th><th>Age</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>David</td><td style="text-align:center">Dog</td><td>4</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>Kitto</td><td style="text-align:center">Cat</td><td>4</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;h2&gt;有兩種解決的方法&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;在資料庫支援的情況下, 以Documention為輔完成任務&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;沒有資料庫不支援的情況下, 將Json的每個key拆開變成獨立的表格, 並加上ID建立所謂的關係來連結不同的表格&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;f
      
    
